name: Onesignal
tagline: Let's code together and make something meaningful
body:
# One Signal 
One is third party push notification API. It is basically used to send notification with some advance feature. Like 

1. send notification to near by location. we can set range up to certain. 

2. send remainder notification.

3. set icon image

    set small icon 
    set big icon 
    set notification banner image

###  Developer Contributor 

we want developer who can explore one signal feature.
